                    <span>This book provides a tight, insightful introduction to ATL programming for the windows programmer moving to COM via ATL. Its also extremely useful as a reference tool.<P>A won't regret purchase and addition to the programmer's bookshelf.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">An essential reference for aspiring ATL programmers.</div>
